OL,5,G0005 999: On the Front Line
OL,6,     FParamedics rush to a 10-year-old
OL,7,     Fboy having a major epileptic fit.
OL,8,     FAn elderly woman struggles to
OL,9,     Fbreathe. And paramedics are called
OL,10,     Fto a man with extreme anxiety.
OL,11,G0110 24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     FKin, who has motor neurone
OL,13,     Fdisease, is rushed to St George's
OL,14,     Fwith severe sepsis. Steve has
OL,15,     Fsevered three fingers with an
OL,16,     Felectric saw. And teenager Jordan
OL,17,     Fhas been in a car crash.
